name: CELEBRATE
description:
A pleasure to be present in celebrations, especially birthday celebrations. On a special day, you get older and become more mature. Demanded to be wiser and smarter, but not all can do both. Being an adult is not an easy matter, it takes effort and time to master it. With a heavy heart we have to go through it,
there is nothing we can do to avoid it. Therefore, if we can get through it well then we will get a good reward later.
December 2nd is my birthday, so I decided to make this something special. thank you for supporting!
